# agent/component Directory Guide

The [agent/component/](mdc:agent/component) directory contains individual agent components, each implementing a specific capability or integration. Notable files include:

- [retrieval.py](mdc:agent/component/retrieval.py): Retrieval component logic.
- [template.py](mdc:agent/component/template.py): Template management for agents.
- [wikipedia.py](mdc:agent/component/wikipedia.py): Wikipedia integration.
- [rewrite.py](mdc:agent/component/rewrite.py): Text rewriting logic.
- [switch.py](mdc:agent/component/switch.py): Component switching logic.
- [generate.py](mdc:agent/component/generate.py): Text generation logic.
- [base.py](mdc:agent/component/base.py): Base class for agent components.
- [email.py](mdc:agent/component/email.py): Email integration.
- [google.py](mdc:agent/component/google.py): Google search integration.
- [bing.py](mdc:agent/component/bing.py): Bing search integration.
- [baidu.py](mdc:agent/component/baidu.py): Baidu search integration.

See each referenced file for more details on the specific component's logic and integration.
